-- Putin says Russia must diversify its economy
-- 
-- Thu Dec 18, 2014 04:45AM EST
-- None



MOSCOW, Dec 18 (Reuters) - President Vladimir Putin said on Thursday that Russia needed to take the opportunity to diversify its economy to protect it from external shocks.

He told his annual end-of-year news conference: "Current external conditions are spurring us on, will make us more effective, switch us to the innovative development path."